{"tid":2335782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】廢老唔帶口罩四圍咳！！！","createTime":"2020-12-22T06:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T11:32:32.000Z","uid":185416,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d48ea8187f3bf08dd0a5556b54693154323c902","tid":2335782,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F2TFBSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF2TFBSE.jpg&h=3a8d8483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解啲廢老咁鍾意除口罩咳？？？？<br />\n咁你帶住個口罩嚟有撚用咩<br />\n咳完之後又帶番個口罩<br />\n即係你個口罩係攞嚟裝飾？？！！<br />\n<br />\n我認為呢啲仆街必須死<br />\n唔知有咩辦法可以懲罰呢班仆街<br />\n唯有將佢哋放上網公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ee737d8783ad5de1831ce59ab1052adbeb4810","tid":2335782,"uid":185416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"最撚戇鳩係佢本身帶住口罩<br />\n想咳嘅時候就除口罩<br />\n呢啲仆街真係防不勝防<br />\n如果一開始見佢冇戴口罩都唔敢坐佢隔離<br />\n最戇鳩係佢一開始有，咳嘅時候先唔帶"},{"pid":"64ba8a7217f6baccab1a967ac1d29fd51a8c9564","tid":2335782,"uid":47614,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"樓主唔夠膽屌廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93aab392fb0e3c7f301b83ba4c418ed7280d68e9","tid":2335782,"uid":130901,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"cit